      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly impeccable condition. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to showroom standards, exhibiting flawless paintwork and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Mechanically superior and rigorously inspected, this automobile represents the pinnacle of its class, offering the sophisticated driver a rare combination of performance and preserved elegance. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
