    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-overhead-cam valvetrain with Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing prophylaxis. Every component, from the Sachs dampers to the cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak mechanical alignment. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cabin maintains the original matte finish on all touchpoints. This is a mechanically sorted, investment-grade driver's car.",
